no quak damag at chuquicamata - mine spokesman the earthquak which hit northern chile today , regist 7.0 on the open-end richter scale , cau no damag to the copper mine at chuquicamata , a mine spokesman said . chuquicamata public relat director guillermo barcelo told reuter by telephon from the mine that the quak had cau no problem and oper continu as usual . a spokesman for the state chilean copper commiss in santiago confirm there had been no damag at chuquicamata .